'''All India Socialist Youth Council''' was a political youth movement in India. It was the youth wing of [[Samajwadi Janata Party]]. The president of AISYC 1992–1996 was Bakta Charan Das.<ref>[http://parliamentofindia.nic.in/ls/lok11/biodata/11or12.htm Biographical Sketch<!-- Bot generated title -->]</ref>

