'''Dominican Postal Institute''' ({{Lang-es|'''Instituto Postal Dominicano'''}}; '''INPOSDOM''') is the [[Dominican Republic|Dominican]] [[institution]] charged with making a more reliable [[Mail|postal service]] for the [[Dominican Republic]]. 

Apart from postal services, INPOSDOM offers [[email]] services for all citizens of the Dominican Republic.

